33
00:03:56.193 --> 00:03:58.177
Aku menimpuknya!

34
00:03:58.297 --> 00:04:00.131
Hebat, Ayumi!

35
00:04:00.360 --> 00:04:01.741
Astaga.

36
00:04:01.861 --> 00:04:03.741
