Ayo pulang. Aku lapar.

78
00:06:52.294 --> 00:06:53.861
Hei!

79
00:06:54.627 --> 00:06:55.874
Kakak Aya!

80
00:06:55.994 --> 00:06:59.541
-Apa kalian senang bermain di salju? -Ya, itu menyenangkan!

81
00:06:59.661 --> 00:07:03.661
